<br>
If equality in damage over time is their goal, it's not hard at all, though it would be unfair to say &quot;half their style bonuses or double ours&quot;.<br>
<br>
OK, they've given LA a 25% nerf across the board? Then give us a 15-20% (remembering that our mainhand base damage is usually more than the LA mainhand) style increase across the board in CDW styles- the maths speak for itself. We are still this far off equality. It's a huge gap.<br>
<br>
